headline: Gaza Strip closed to Israelis
description: The commander of the IDF southern command, Maj. Gen. Dan Harel, has declared the Gaza Strip a closed military zone. The army will consider applications to enter the Strip on an individual basis. (Hanan Greenberg)
articleBody: The commander of the IDF southern command, Maj. Gen. Dan Harel, has declared the Gaza Strip a closed military zone. The army will consider applications to enter the Strip on an individual basis. (Hanan Greenberg)
